What are my flatmates eating today?

Living with flatmates has been fun,seeing them cook such diverse type of food made me wonder how often they eat that certain type of food.

Making ordinary observations about my flatmates eating habits interesting and easy to understand. Instead of just listing what food they ate, I found clever ways to connect different pieces of information to tell a story.

This Report shows summaries about the observation.
